<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN"
  "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">

<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en" lang="en">
<head>
  <!-- <%= server_name %> -->
  <meta http-equiv="Content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
  <%= meta_description %>
  <%= meta_keywords %>

  
  <title><%= view_title %></title>
  
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag('get_started', :media => 'screen, projection') %>
  
  <%= javascript_include_tag(:defaults, :cache => true) %>

</head>

<body id="customer">
<div id="mainWrapper">
  <div id="header">
    <%= image_tag('logo.png', :alt => 'Renewzle') %>
    
    <div id="taglineWrapper">
      <%= image_tag('tagline.png', :alt => 'Renewable Energy Made Easy') %>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div id="content">
    <div id="leftContent">
      <%= image_tag('customer/solarPower.jpg', :alt => 'Would Solar Power Work For My House?') %>
      
      <div id="arrowContainer">
        <%= image_tag('customer/choose-the-right-system.jpg', :alt => 'Choose the right solar system for your home and compare quotes from installers in your area.') %>
        <%= image_tag('customer/arrows828.jpg', :alt => 'Learn => Explore => Shop') %>

        <div class="arrows learn">
          <p class="bottom">Visit Renewzle&rsquo;s <a href="http://<%= server_name %>/learn">Solar Information Library</a> to find hundreds of articles with practical information and advice about solar and renewable energy technologies. Topics include:</p>
          
          <ul>
            <li><a href="http://<%= server_name %>/learn/about/how-solar-works">How Solar Works</a></li>
            <li><a href="http://<%= server_name %>/learn/about/solar-and-you">Solar &amp; You</a></li>
            <li><a href="http://<%= server_name %>/learn/about/solar-and-renewable-energy-policy">Solar &amp; Renewable Energy Policy</a></li>
            <li><a href="http://<%= server_name %>/learn/about/other-solar-technology">Other Solar Technology</a></li>
            <li>&hellip;and more!</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="arrows explore">
          <p>Renewzle&rsquo;s solar power calculator helps you explore your solar options with the most comprehensive solar financial analysis available.</p>
          
          <p>You can adjust your profile to reflect your needs and budget and find the best solar system for your home.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="arrows shop">
          <p>Shop for quotes from system retailers and installers.</p>
          
          <p>Once you know what you want, Renewzle is the ONLY service that allows you to get multiple bids from retailers in your area, without leaving your home or revealing your personal information.When you choose the perfect system, Renewzle will find the perfect retailer and the perfect price!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="rightContent">
      <div id="formContainer">
        <div id="get_started_form" class="callout">
          <div class="top-left">
            <div class="bottom-right">
	            <h3 class="top-right">Get started with a free, personalized<br />
 solar financial analysis now...</h3>
              
              <% @page_javascript << "Form.focusFirstElement('#{dom_id(@profile)}');" -%>
              <% labelled_form_for(@profile, :url => profile_path, :loading => "showItemLoadingFor('profile');") do |profile_form| -%>
      					<p style="margin:0;padding:0">
      		      	<%= profile_form.hidden_field(:street_address) %>
      		      </p>	
    		      	<%= profile_form.labelled_text_field(:postal_code, :label => 'Zip code', :error_label => 'Zip') %>

            		<div class="bottom-left">
              		<p class="bottom"><%= image_submit_tag('customer/getStartedButton.jpg', :alt => 'Get Started', :class => 'button') %></p>
            		</div>
      			  <% end -%>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <small>Renewzle&rsquo;s solar calculator is only available to California homeowners at this time. To receive updates when we expand to other states and add new features, and to stay up to date with renewable energy news, please <a href="https://app.streamsend.com/public/CaUn/YGr/subscribe">sign up for our mailing list</a>.</small>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
  
<div id="footer">
  <hr />
</div>

<div id="subFooter">        
  <ul id="courtesy_navi">
    <li><%= link_to('About Us', about_url) %> <%= separator %></li>
    <li><%= link_to('Press', press_url) %> <%= separator %></li>
    <li><%= link_to('How Renewzle Works', how_renewzle_works_url) %> <%= separator %></li>
    <li><%= link_to('FAQ', faq_url, :title => 'Renewzle FAQ') %> <%= separator %></li>
    <li><%= link_to('Privacy Policy', privacy_policy_url) %> <%= separator %></li>
    <li><%= link_to('Terms of Service', tos_url) %> <%= separator %></li>
    <li><%= link_to('Retailer Signup', partner_signup_url) %></li>
    <li style="margin-left:2em"><%= link_to('Login', login_url) %></li>
  </ul>
      
	Copyright &copy; 2008 Renewzle, Inc. All rights reserved.
</div>

<%= page_javascript %>
<%= google_analytics %>

</body>
</html>
